<%= render :partial => "page_side_panel" %>
<div id="spotus_page">
     <h2>Quick Donate</h2>
     <p>
     Do you want to support journalism but don't have the time to go through all the <%=h SITE_NAME%> pitches to find the right one?
     </p>
     <p>
     Now you can donate to beats and <%=h SITE_NAME%> promises that any money donated to these beats will be used ONLY for reporting within those subjects.
     </p>
     <ul>
         <li>
           Donate to
           <%= link_to "Environment Reporting", "http://spot.us/pitches/183" %>
         </li>    
         <li>
           Donate to 
           <%= link_to "Education Reporting", "http://spot.us/pitches/182" %>
         </li>
         <li>
           Donate to local   
           <%= link_to "Political Reporting", "http://spot.us/pitches/184" %>
         </li>
     </ul>
     <p>
       Didn't see the topic you want to support? Let us know:
       <%= mail_to APP_CONFIG[:email_notifications][:info][:email], nil, :encode => "hex" %>
     </p>
</div>
